net.minecraftforge.fml.common.LoaderExceptionModCrash: Caught exception from VmeOnOpenPlayerInventory (vmeonopenplayerinventory)
Caused by: java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError: net/minecraft/client/gui/GuiScreen
删除E.jar，也就是VmeOnOpenPlayerInventory这个mod
这个mod用到了客户端才有的类，而服务端并没有这个类
